overview.en: Fox IM is a social platform based on blockchain network, which can realize the free switching between traditional network social and P2P peer-to-peer networks, and can achieve decentralized and absolute private chat. And developed a mobile application based on FOX network, integrating social, information, finance, entertainment and cloud wallet.
overview.zh: Fox IM是基于区块链网络的社交平台，可以实现传统网络社交和P2P对等网络之间的自由切换，可以实现去中心的，绝对的私密聊天。并开发出基于FOX网络，集社交，资讯，金融，娱乐，云钱包于一体的移动应用。
